snippet: The Fed chairwoman described the valuations of smaller firms and biotech and social media companies as “stretched.”
abstract: Stock market pulls back, giving up early gains after Federal Reserve chairwoman Janet L Yellen raises concerns before congressional panel about some market sectors.
lead_paragraph: The Fed chairwoman described the valuations of smaller firms and biotech and social media companies as “stretched.”

headline.main: Shares Mostly Decline After Fed Chief’s Warning
